{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01FxS4htq5eBr7pJ7QCqNZVW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. I need to:\n\n1. Add a new route `GET /projects/{name}/runs` in handler.go that serves the runs list filtered by project\n2. Update template links from `/runs?project={{.Dir}}` to `/projects/{{.Label}}/runs`\n3. Update the runs.html JavaScript `filterByProject` to use the new URL pattern\n4. Update the run_detail.html breadcrumb link\n5. Update tests that reference the old URL\n\nLet me think about the approach:\n\n- The new route `GET /projects/{name}/runs` should resolve the project label to a directory, then render the runs page filtered by that project.\n\n\n- I'll create a new handler that extracts the project name from the URL path, resolves it to its directory, and then reuses the existing runs list logic. I should also scan for any other places where `/runs?project=` is referenced to make sure I update them all.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12036,"cache_read_input_tokens":44584,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12036},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"16a46129-8131-4a0d-a280-411fa357c435","uuid":"7161579a-e07e-4728-9089-0652774647f4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01FxS4htq5eBr7pJ7QCqNZVW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture. Here's what needs to change:\n\n1. **Route**: Add `GET /projects/{name}/runs` \n2. **Handler**: New handler that resolves project label to dir, then renders runs\n3. **Templates**: Update links from `/runs?project={{.Dir}}` to `/projects/{{.Label}}/runs`\n4. **Tests**: Update test URLs\n\nLet me implement this."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12036,"cache_read_input_tokens":44584,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12036},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"16a46129-8131-4a0d-a280-411fa357c435","uuid":"27bc6434-c76c-4c0a-9abb-04d743acdd3a"}
